 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Year                  Capital         Units        Income
                     retained      encashed      received
                     (Pounds)      (Pounds)      (Pounds)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
1993                    9,225           775        817.63
1994                    8,500           725        814.61
1995                    7,825           675        821.12
1996                    7,200           625        834.67
1997                      n/a         7,200        826.33
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
