Sir, Your headline read 'PM rejects European super state' (April 29).
Doesn't any one think it in the least odd that while Mr Major, the prime
minister, and Mr Douglas Hurd, the foreign secretary, continue to reject a
United States of Europe in the federal mould, Tory members of the European
