federal unification and integration in Europe and . . . the realisation of
United States of Europe'.
Odder still that the EPP expects them to stand as Christian Democrats at the
next European elections in 1994.
The EPP claims to be 'The Heart of Europe'. That is where Mr Major says he
wants to be. Coincidence? Or is the Tory party about to change its name?
Anthony Kinch,
