aviation, investment protection, broadcasting and help for small and
medium-scale enterprises in Ashkhabad.
Turkmenistan will switch to a Latin-based Turkish alphabet from the Cyrillic
script imposed by Moscow decades ago to strengthen control over Central
Asia.
